\f1\b\fs28 \cf2 \strokec2 3. The Scalability Bottleneck (And how to fix it)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf2 The Risk:
\f0\b0  Generating 3 full website designs with AI takes time (maybe 10-30 seconds). Standard web requests time out after 10 seconds. If 100 people do this at once, your server might choke.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf2 The Solution:
\f0\b0  
\f1\b Asynchronous Processing (Queues)
