\cf2 This is a fantastic architectural decision. Moving the "Generation Pipeline" to 
\f1\b n8n
\f0\b0  is a game-changer because it solves the #1 problem with AI SaaS: 
\f1\b Timeouts
\f0\b0 .\
Next.js (Vercel) will time out after 10-60 seconds. Generating a full website with images takes 2-3 minutes. n8n solves this by handling the long-running process in the background.\
Here is your updated 
\f1\b PressPilot Architecture
\f0\b0  with n8n as the "Brain" and the new Image Generation Pipeline.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

