\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Next.js saves a record to Supabase: \cf3 \cb12 \strokec3 projects\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2  table (Status: 'processing').\
\ls32\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
