\f0\b0\fs24 \cf2 This is your strongest fail-safe. If your AI is generating complex layouts (like custom SVG dividers, complex CSS grids, or artistic layouts) that standard Blocks struggle with, 
\f1\b do not
\f0\b0  try to force them into Group blocks.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
